'From Squeak3.2alpha of 2 October 2001 [latest update: #4413] on 3 October 2001 at 12:22:18 pm'!"Change Set:		setNatLangFix-swDate:			3 October 2001Author:			Scott WallaceA fix repeated here for the benefit of earlier adopters of update 4353, into which this method was recently patched"!!CategoryViewer methodsFor: 'categories' stamp: 'sw 9/27/2001 21:44'!setNaturalLanguageTo: aLanguage	"Set the natural language symbol as indicated"	chosenCategorySymbol ifNil: [^ self delete].	self updateCategoryNameTo: ((self currentVocabulary ifNil: [Vocabulary eToyVocabulary]) categoryWordingAt: chosenCategorySymbol)! !